text: Elisa Bozzo (born 8 May 1987) is an Italian synchronised swimmer. She competed in the team event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. Bozzo is an athlete of the Gruppo Sportivo della Marina Militare. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Italian synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Italy Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Artistic swimmers of Marina Militare
